<plot>Convicted of murder in the assisted suicide of his ailing wife, David has but one visitor to his death row cell just moments before he is to die. Doubt, in the form of a taunting and insidious character, confronts David with the intentions he had on that fateful day. Was it love or something far darker that drove him to take the life of his wife? David must face up to the demons of his past in the battle for his soul before the clock counts down to his impending execution.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?245396</url></doc>
